{"tid":1565701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中秋有感] 大家今晚賞月嗰陣 心入面要諗住一班義士","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T13:56:53.000Z","uid":266736,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0401c8eda6081601c219bdd32c90902be1fe477e","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"當我哋諗緊今晚食完飯 去邊唱歌好嘅同時<br />\n好多人已經唔可以正常咁過節....<br />\n傷到郁唔返 / 仲休養緊<br />\n甚至連屋企都返唔到 /<br />\n被屋企人割席 / 經濟被截斷<br />\n去咗台灣嘅義士 /<br />\n仲有9位 甚至係更加多位 連個月光都再無機會見到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家今晚唱歌/賞月嘅同時<br />\n心入面諗一諗起佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話想好sad咁過節 / 一定要做d咩<br />\n不過至少諗一諗起佢哋 <br />\n咁如果行動上可以去悼念義士就更加好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">To 義士們：<br />\n加油呀 香港人支持你哋 希望你哋平安 <br />\n遠方嘅你哋要幸福呀 香港人會幫你行埋落去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">亦都祝香港人好人一生平安 我哋會贏㗎！</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"af0473e4dff9bbbfba683a05efc1656a14406d6c","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137eb3ca8d4a4e408168b6542bf61088ca573a0d","tid":1565701,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺係無窗架 連賞月都無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5b68c37cdbc79df34cd99645c779895a69e2b0","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"這個中秋不快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e37041e74e6993c9063330305a2c9feeb0a3d73","tid":1565701,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[光復香港]觀塘中秋放映會，今晚見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565670\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565670</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位觀塘友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556b9d1a8449d7b72e69764bcab5a0196f8a13f8","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fa816f1b7999d26a39c171016b25e15f3854fe","tid":1565701,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"大家今晚賞月果陣<br />\n間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住既ＴＶＢ <br />\n將會不斷loop「暴徒」「暴徒」「暴徒」<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6008124412be60d35500e8edd1f76cf242a88468","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e2017854169fdfe440b40379595f4eaf346bf9","tid":1565701,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid